{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-topic-js","path":"/topics/nirvana/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"nodes":[{"excerpt":"Beyond learning and unlearning is awareness, and beyond awareness is consciousness, and beyond consciousness is immortality, and beyond immortality is dharma and beyond dharma is nirvana.","fields":{"slug":"/quotes/12/"},"image":null,"placeholder":{"patternFile":{"publicURL":"/static/22efd708a9aaa591db0ba5f725e9c08b/bubbles-merging.svg"},"foregroundColor":"#F35F00","backgroundColor":"#DF3A0A"}},{"excerpt":"By fully focusing your mind on your chakras, stilling your thoughts, and increasing your kundalini flow, you can rise above your body consciousness and unite your mind with the clear light of nirvana.","fields":{"slug":"/quotes/15/"},"image":null,"placeholder":{"patternFile":{"publicURL":"/static/d10e23a6392478f0a0ca7883e84eef29/mosaic-harmony.svg"},"foregroundColor":"#D88508","backgroundColor":"#DF3A0A"}},{"excerpt":"Enlightenment occurs when your mind merges with nirvana, with what Tibetans call the dharmakaya, the clear light of reality, which is the highest plane of transcendental wisdom and perfectâ€¦","fields":{"slug":"/quotes/18/"},"image":null,"placeholder":{"patternFile":{"publicURL":"/static/22efd708a9aaa591db0ba5f725e9c08b/bubbles-merging.svg"},"foregroundColor":"#b50047","backgroundColor":"#FFB910"}},{"excerpt":"Your mind is made up of light. We call it the dharmakaya, the clear light of reality. The transcendental eternal light is everywhere. It's the light of god or whatever you want to call it.","fields":{"slug":"/quotes/19/"},"image":null,"placeholder":{"patternFile":{"publicURL":"/static/2ec08a32396579340a090c9bbeea7601/intersecting-waves.svg"},"foregroundColor":"#DF3A0A","backgroundColor":"#D88508"}},{"excerpt":"In Tantric Buddhism, we believe that Samsara is Nirvana. That is to say that everything in the universe is part of us. And we also are part of everything in the universe.","fields":{"slug":"/quotes/58/"},"image":null,"placeholder":{"patternFile":{"publicURL":"/static/505dd367d624c76d9bbba09c8282cfed/merging-fibers.svg"},"foregroundColor":"#F35F00","backgroundColor":"#FFB910"}}]},"file":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.5,"src":"/static/f06c23b75c114f6a2fb9860fb210de7d/7d509/Nirvana.jpg","srcSet":"/static/f06c23b75c114f6a2fb9860fb210de7d/9104c/Nirvana.jpg 480w,\n/static/f06c23b75c114f6a2fb9860fb210de7d/7d509/Nirvana.jpg 720w","sizes":"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px"}}}},"pageContext":{"topic":"Nirvana"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1034268292","3159128766"]}